AWP - Any(event) Web Publish version 0.01
=========================================

This is a template language.
It's like lift, but in perl and vaguer.

Track issues at http://circl.lighthouseapp.com/projects/41103-awp

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Sisyphus 0.01

